-- Ex-UBS Trader Adoboli of Ghana Pleads Not Guilty Over Unauthorized Trades
-- B y   L i n d s a y   F o r t a d o   a n d   B e n   M o s h i n s k y
-- 2012-01-30T10:18:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-30/ex-ubs-trader-adoboli-of-ghana-pleads-not-guilty-over-unauthorized-trades.html
Kweku Adoboli, the former  UBS AG (UBSN) 
trader who is accused of causing the largest loss from
unauthorized trading in British history, pleaded not guilty to
fraud and false accounting.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lindsay Fortado in London at 
